✨ 5 lucky winners will have a chance to win products worth ₹5-7K each!
This giveaway is open to everyone and includes a variety of skincare, haircare, and body care & makeup goodies—perfect for you or to share with your dear ones!

Here’s how to enter:
1️⃣ Follow me on Instagram.
2️⃣ Like this post.
3️⃣ Comment below sharing one thing you love about my content & tag a friend/family member you’d like to share these goodies with.
4️⃣ (Optional) Share this post on your story and tag me so I can see it!

Important Details:

This giveaway is exclusively for my followers. Non-followers, spam accounts, or entries that don’t follow the rules will not qualify.
If you’re sharing your story, make sure your profile is public so I can see and repost it.
Entries close on [24th December], and winners will be announced the same day!
Thank you for being a part of this incredible journey. Good luck! ✨
